        <name>libvlc_errmsg</name>
        <param>
          <type>void</type>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>A human-readable error message for the last LibVLC error in the calling thread. The resulting string is valid until another error occurs (at least until the next LibVLC call).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="warning"><para>This will be NULL if there was no error. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
